
Creating Service Types

The structure of the service types is a trees. It is important when 
the services a being select during the contract signing. There are
filters that allows selecting services only from a single tree of
types. This is useful when we describe dependencies between the 
service, when one service requires another.  

place:
Administration / Services

types: 

 - Internet
   - sub service type(depending of the internet service)
 - TV 
 - Internet + TV (Bundle)

















